    "Tooltip.LABEL[C2VM.TrafficLightsEnhancement.Dynamic]": "Dynamiczna sygnalizacja zmienia cykle i dostosowuje czas w zależności od natężenia ruchu.",
    "Tooltip.LABEL[C2VM.TrafficLightsEnhancement.FixedTimed]": "Fixed timing mode with preset phase durations.",
    "Tooltip.LABEL[C2VM.TrafficLightsEnhancement.SmartPhaseSelection]": "Włącz inteligentny wybór cykli w zależności od natężenia ruchu. Wyłącz, aby ustawić prostą sekwencję (1→2→3→4→1...).",
    "Tooltip.LABEL[C2VM.TrafficLightsEnhancement.Auto]": "Automatically balances traffic flow and waiting time to decide when to change phase.",
    "Tooltip.LABEL[C2VM.TrafficLightsEnhancement.OnFlowDrop]": "Changes phase when traffic flow decreases. Keeps traffic moving smoothly.",
    "Tooltip.LABEL[C2VM.TrafficLightsEnhancement.OnWaitIncrease]": "Changes phase when waiting traffic increases. Reduces wait times.",
    "Tooltip.LABEL[C2VM.TrafficLightsEnhancement.WhenEmpty]": "Changes phase only when current lanes are empty. Maximizes throughput per phase.",
    "Tooltip.LABEL[C2VM.TrafficLightsEnhancement.WhenNoDemand]": "Changes phase only when other lanes have waiting traffic. Avoids unnecessary changes.",
    "Tooltip.LABEL[C2VM.TrafficLightsEnhancement.WaitSensitivity]": "How much to prioritize waiting traffic. Higher = change phases sooner when cars are waiting.",
    "Tooltip.LABEL[C2VM.TrafficLightsEnhancement.MinimumDuration]": "Ustaw minimalny czas, w którym cykl świetlny musi być aktywny, zanim będzie mógł się zmienić, niezależnie od natężenia ruchu.",
    "Tooltip.LABEL[C2VM.TrafficLightsEnhancement.MaximumDuration]": "Sets the maximum time a traffic light phase can remain active. This prevents a phase from staying green too long when there is no traffic waiting.",
    "Tooltip.LABEL[C2VM.TrafficLightsEnhancement.TargetDuration]": "Scales the calculated target duration for each phase. The target duration is calculated as: 10 * (AverageCarFlow + TrackLaneOccupied * 0.5) * TargetDurationMultiplier. Higher values make phases last longer.",
    "Tooltip.LABEL[C2VM.TrafficLightsEnhancement.IntervalExponent]": "Controls how aggressively the system prioritizes phases that haven't run recently. Higher values make phases that haven't run for a long time get much higher priority, ensuring fair rotation.",
    "Tooltip.LABEL[C2VM.TrafficLightsEnhancement.CarWeight]": "Mnożnik wagi dla pasów ruchu samochodowego, przy obliczaniu priorytetu cyklów. Wyższe wartości nadają priorytetu dla cyklu z oczekującymi pojazdami.",
    "Tooltip.LABEL[C2VM.TrafficLightsEnhancement.BusWeight]": "Weight multiplier for public transport (bus) lanes. Higher values prioritize buses over regular traffic.",
    "Tooltip.LABEL[C2VM.TrafficLightsEnhancement.TrackWeight]": "Mnożnik wagi dla torów tramwajowych/kolejowych. Wyższe wartości nadają priorytetu dla cyklu z oczekującymi pojazdami szynowymi.",
    "Tooltip.LABEL[C2VM.TrafficLightsEnhancement.PedestrianWeight]": "Mnożnik wagi dla przejść dla pieszych.",
    "Tooltip.LABEL[C2VM.TrafficLightsEnhancement.SmoothingFactor]": "How much to blend current calculations with previous values. 0 = no smoothing (instant changes), 1 = full smoothing (very gradual changes).",
    "Tooltip.LABEL[C2VM.TrafficLightsEnhancement.Flow]": "Average car flow through this phase.",
    "Tooltip.LABEL[C2VM.TrafficLightsEnhancement.FlowRatio]": "Smoothed flow ratio for phase decisions.",
    "Tooltip.LABEL[C2VM.TrafficLightsEnhancement.WaitRatio]": "Smoothed wait ratio for phase decisions.",
    "Tooltip.LABEL[C2VM.TrafficLightsEnhancement.WeightedWaiting]": "Combined waiting metric used for phase priority."
